> c. 440 ABY [citation needed]

### Notable Events

- Ok'dakie battles a cancer-like dark side malady contracted from the potion created by Nathyra
- The Sith splinter into factions and tensions begin to rise
- Izen creates a university on Tython to train Force sensitives
- Astaroth fills the power vacuum left by Savage's death and assumes the title of Dark Lord
- Astaroth begins a campaign of scorching planets
- Lexdaela is freed from slavery


- Lexdaela becomes Grandmaster
